                     Thomas Challis, Esq.; Thomas Sidney, Esq., M.P.; Francis Graham Moon, Esq.; Thomas Quested Finnis, Esq.; and Robert Walter Carden, Esq.; Aldermen of the said City: John Mirehouse, Esq., Common-Serjeant of the said City; and 


